channel.title: Moparscape.org will not run
channel.description: I have asked this to many people. When I downloaded the new JAVA 1.6.0_01 I was following one of those tutorials that said download the latest. I did mess with system variables. Any way wen I click on the moparscape link on my desktop(Idownloaded the client thing)It comes up wit a message that says "Can not find Main Class. Program will exit." Someone told me that it was because someone renamed my MANIFEST file. Does anyone know what that is? I also try to go to http://www.moparisthebest.com It comes up wit a big white square screen. It still has the advertisements and the links for server status and the forums. Really quik a little orange square pops up in the top left hand corner of the white square. I think it has something to do wit java. I also tried to play the game called runescape. When I got to the login screen It is a big white square too. The same orange square appears in the top left white screen. I read a help thing on runescape and it says that when u pick low or high detail at the bottem of the screen change the little box from "Signed Applet Using Defualt Java(recommended)" to "Unsigned Applet Using Default java" And then when I go to the logon screen(name and pass) After about 10-15seconds it will load (slower than it used to b),but it works. Does anyone knowhow to fix my java or how to use moparscape. I cant login:( Please help me. anbudy want to help me or take a guess. I cant do much except post without bein able to login

item.title: Moparscape.org will not run
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

First of all, you should re-download Java. A direct link to the download page can be found here. Select to download “JDK 6u1”. Accept the license agreement and select to download the “Offline Multi-language installation”.

When the download is finished you may want to change your Envirnment Variables. For a tutorial on doing such a thing click here. This tutorial is made by Alexia and full credits are to him.

If you have any problems, concerns/comments please feel free to PM me or post it here.

–Tico135–
